msgid "*This line sets up a sketching context.*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/tutorial_design.rst:234
msgid ""
"sort_by(Axis.Y) *sorts the faces along the Y-axis, arranging them from the "
"lowest Y-coordinate to the highest.*"
